\v 18 ya kumi na moja ikamwangukia Azareli,\f + \fr 25:18 \ft Azareli jina lingine ni Uzieli.\f* //wanawe na jamaa zake, \tcr2 12
\tr \tc1
\v 19 ya kumi na mbili ikamwangukia Hashabia, //wanawe na jamaa zake, \tcr2 12
\tr \tc1
\v 20 ya kumi na tatu ikamwangukia Shubaeli, //wanawe na jamaa zake, \tcr2 12
\tr \tc1
\v 21 ya kumi na nne ikamwangukia Matithia, //wanawe na jamaa zake, \tcr2 12
\tr \tc1
\v 22 ya kumi na tano ikamwangukia Yeremothi, //wanawe na jamaa zake, \tcr2 12
\tr \tc1
